一體機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T16:11:26.000Z","msg":"最後買左呢隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xnFN0Z1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxnFN0Z1.png&h=9888fd91&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d65fb05a1d3125a1e49bdb7668501a8ca34a7e0f","tid":1049452,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af0f0a2ccc3f4eb907f57a318164040e3bbd0e39","tid":1049452,"uid":167879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T09:28:33.000Z","msg":"Toyota Camry 2.4<br />\n約一千左右<br />\n搵左款，但客服又話香港車用唔到<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WnCo8xh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWnCo8xh.png&h=29701484&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T19:43:09.000Z","msg":"講明先， 而家大陸android機 係平功能強。<br />\n但音質大多都好差， 就算用7850 廣音ic都只係好些少。 講就50w x4 @4ohm ,但一般力水都好唔平衡，而且最大問題係android本身就只得2路 output , 係内置mixer做前後balance , 但效果幾差。 要改善音質就得加power amp , 但rca只多2路無法分前後。<br />\n<br />\n一般黎講音質仲差過一般日系單頭機，我3部車都换哂大mon android機，但為左呢個問題洗唔少錢先得返原有音質。<br />\n其中一個方案係中間再接入一個比較貴o既dsp mixer, 由籃牙用手機設置，再入返4路power amp出揚聲器，但隻dsp都千幾銀。<br />\n<br />\n唯一好處係android機直接4g上網，也有wifi , 乜apps都可用，又可以同手機同步。<br />\n線路對接相對簡單，有經驗o既人基本diy搞掂。<br />\n<br />\n第二部車我試驗性用高轉低電平 接返amp,  質素可接受但也不算很好，好處係唔使加dsp mixer省錢。<br />\n<br />\n而家android機有專用dvd或bd rom , 插usb就讀到碟。<br />\n<br />\nbtw我set左個nas係屋企，只要一開機就會自動sync個歌庫同mtv庫，平時係屋企down好就得。"},{"pid":"6e811a0c632f2085efc347b399247e90e823d26a","tid":1049452,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9862fcfa4b532fe17e3620c875be24bad75825d","tid":1049452,"uid":59821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01f730725034ad82eb6832fd26ea0595bcf0ee0d","tid":1049452,"uid":123177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b892c30a8059fa406016c63cd68b87d4367883a6","tid":1049452,"uid":167879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:41:20.000Z","msg":"聲音要求唔高，旨在有導航"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:51:27.000Z","msg":"大廠 吉個android /iPhon